Hydro is implemented in C++. To include Hydro in a project use...

#include <hydro/hydro.hpp>

...to include all public headers. See /docs/Setup.md for details
regarding initialization of the HvmEnv, a foreign function
interface necessary for interacting with the virtual machine.
